### Task 7: CSV Parser — Parse, Validate, Build Trade Ledger ✅
- `portfolio_doctor/core/csv_parser.py` — full pipeline: parse → validate → build
- `parse_csv()` — CSV reader with column validation, date parsing, normalization
- `validate_trades()` — oversell, duplicate, weekend warnings (pure, no network)
- `validate_symbols()` — equity via yfinance, MF via mftool (network-dependent, separate)
- `build_position_ledger()` — FIFO for equity (avg_cost tracking), per-lot for MF (FIFO sell)
- `build_cash_flows()` — signed flows for XIRR (BUY/SIP negative, SELL positive)
- `detect_sip_patterns()` — monthly cadence detection (25–35 day gaps, 60% threshold)
- `tests/portfolio_doctor/core/test_csv_parser.py` — 26 tests (6 parse, 4 validate, 3 symbols, 5 ledger, 4 cashflow, 4 SIP)
- Tests use `monkeypatch` for symbol validation mocking (no pytest-mock dependency)

### Task 8: Portfolio Engine — Holdings, Returns, XIRR, Allocation ✅
- `portfolio_doctor/core/portfolio_engine.py` — the math layer
- `compute_holdings()` — FIFO equity + per-lot MF, as_of date filtering
- `compute_xirr()` — scipy.optimize.brentq solver, returns annualized rate
- `compute_returns()` — per-position returns, portfolio XIRR, total invested/value
- `compute_portfolio_value_series()` — daily values from holdings × prices
- `compute_sector_allocation()` — sector weights + instrument type split
- `compute_turnover()` — sell amounts / avg portfolio value
- `compute_tax_drag()` — STCG (15%) + LTCG (10% above ₹1L) on realized gains
- `compute_cash_flows` — re-export of `csv_parser.build_cash_flows`
- `tests/portfolio_doctor/core/test_portfolio_engine.py` — 27 tests (5 holdings, 5 XIRR, 3 returns, 3 value series, 3 allocation, 3 turnover, 4 tax drag, 1 re-export)

